review_blob: Tap at Kool Keg. Pours a murky reddish orange color. Raspberries on the nose, slight funk. Dry Brett flavor is evident with raspberries playing another role on the flavor. Easy finish.

review_blob: On tap at the brewery. Fruity Pebbles version. Clear light gold appearance. Fruity nose for sure. Smells exactly like a bowl of fruity pebbles would. Perfume flavor however. Limey and citrus. Slightly metallic on the finish. A bit too odd for my tastes.

review_blob: Tap at the brewery. Pours a clear light golden color. Light bread on the nose with some easy fruit. Subtle coriander is also apparent. Easy finish but almost a touch watery.
